            <title>Apple 为 Snoopy 迷送上圣诞礼物，Apple Watch 表面和 Apple TV 4K 萤幕保护程式</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/12/apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/12/apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 06:20:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple tv]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[snoopy]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280920</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>长青的 Snoopy 至今仍然有不少粉丝，而 Apple 最近就宣布推出一系列 Snoopy 主题新功能，包括 Apple Watch 互动表面及 Apple TV 4K 萤幕保护程式，作为圣诞礼物。<br /><span id="more-1280920"></span></p><p>Apple 表示，全新的 Apple Watch 表面以 Snoopy 和 Woodstock 为主角，会与时针互动玩耍，更会根据当地天气变化作出反应，在用户运动时更会展现活力十足的动态效果。同时，在 Apple TV 4K（第二代及以后版本）推出的 Snoopy 萤幕保护程式，则以生动的动画和变化的季节场景呈现，为居家环境增添趣味。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280923" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280924" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280925" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>现在 Apple TV+ 作为《Snoopy 花生漫画》的官方播放平台，有提供多部获奖的原创作品及经典花生漫画作品，包括深受欢迎的《查理布朗的大南瓜》、《查理布朗的感恩节》以及《查理布朗的愉快圣诞》等特别节目，让 Snoopy 迷在圣诞佳节可以在家轻松观赏。</p><p>来源：Apple</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
